               <objectContents>
                  <ab type="description">These are scenes from the home of the family U. The couple is seated on a soffa with their toddler. In some pictures the parents take care of the child, in others the father reads a newspaper while sipping a drink (probably rakija) and the child is on his wooden ponny assisted by the mother, and in some final pictures the child is in his father’s lap. The parents seem in good mood. The interior of this living room is consisted of: sofa, small table, a wooden ponny, a curtain, a tepistry on the wall, a photo camera on the wall, a chair on the side, newspapers and other items.</ab>
               </objectContents>
